Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.32,0:00:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.22,0:00:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫南千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三姐妹的小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时觉得姐姐有一个就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无奈是三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:24.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天全国以晴天为主…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  好好的吐我槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是早已起床了啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被炉里睡觉会感冒的哟什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:32.82,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这就是二女儿夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人如其名  如夏日阳光一样让人厌烦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么能引以为傲的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是在想些什么失礼的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得「夏奈今天也好精神啊」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖暖的暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种依赖被炉的生活打算持续到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被炉却不用  对它可是很失礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好的话  来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞错了  这位是大女儿春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人如其名  如春日阳光一样温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是引以为傲的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么也不能在被炉里换衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐也请说说她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的外套再放里面暖暖么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的制服已经暖好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙打算依赖被炉生活到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被炉却不用  对它可是很失礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  快点换好衣服来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今天也要精精神神地去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会返还试卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼  肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不休息可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要管我了你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试成绩要给我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天休息考试成绩也不会变  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门喽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:17.15,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,300)}春天的开始、南家的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还是那么充满人情味的绝妙分数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能不会令春香满意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回考试不扭转现状就不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  找人教我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我功课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  夏奈不会认真学的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了我这认真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  现在没戴眼镜看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好奇怪  刚才还戴着的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子没有回应我的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  去海边吧去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求别人的时候  比起认真来纯真才更重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪  美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高和我家的千秋差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  纯朴的眼神很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然这么说虽然很失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成绩不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然也太失礼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个让你提高成绩的好提议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  教美雪功课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家教就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好很棒哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我看上的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  这里教我下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己稍微动动脑筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  这里教我下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么光偏袒美雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了教美雪的功课才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  不要那么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过拜托别人得到想要的只适用于小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己的力量去达成目的这才是学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如夏奈所说的我要靠自己的力量努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个气势  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  降了一分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然光靠一个人的力量是不行的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类不互相帮助是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了夏奈  我第一次得了100分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去做就能成功的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我长高的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以  不过要教我功课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类要互相帮助才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  教我功课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
